<br>
I want to be able to raid with my guild without having another guild rubbernecking and seeing how we do things just so they can come do it the next week without working out the tactics themselves (you know who you are). <br>
<br>
I want to see people actually realize a little competition is good and keeps one guild from becoming the FoH of the sever and being a bunch of asses.<br>
<br>
